# ER-диаграмма системы управления задачами

## Основные сущности и связи

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USERS {
        int id PK
        string username UK
        string email UK
        json roles
        string password
        string first_name
        string last_name
        string phone
        string position
        string department
        boolean is_active
        datetime last_login_at
        datetime created_at
        datetime updated_at
    }

    TASKS {
        int id PK
        string title
        text description
        string status
        int priority
        date due_date
        date start_date
        datetime completed_at
        decimal estimated_hours
        decimal actual_hours
        int user_id FK
        int category_id FK
        int parent_id FK
        datetime created_at
        datetime updated_at
    }

    TASK_CATEGORIES {
        int id PK
        string name
        string color
        string icon
        boolean is_active
        int user_id FK
        datetime created_at
    }

    %% Relationships
    USERS ||--o{ TASKS : "creates"
    TASKS }o--|| TASK_CATEGORIES : "belongs_to"
```

